you wanted to have total control over:

1375
01:35:24,830 --> 01:35:26,821
Collins and Morris.

1376
01:35:28,334 --> 01:35:32,430
You made me abandon any thought
of trying to contact Lanny.

1377
01:35:33,039 --> 01:35:35,439
You made me feel like I was
less than nothing to him...

1378
01:35:35,641 --> 01:35:37,802
...because you were playing
your own complex game.

1379
01:35:38,010 --> 01:35:43,710
And what exactly was this complex
game I was playing, Miss O'Connor?

1380
01:36:02,335 --> 01:36:03,996
You were in the room.

1381
01:36:05,338 --> 01:36:07,067
That night.

1382
01:36:07,807 --> 01:36:10,503
Lanny had a robe.
He dropped it on the bed.

1383
01:36:10,710 --> 01:36:13,304
After Maureen asked for money...

1384
01:36:13,512 --> 01:36:15,480
...the wallet was on top.
It had been folded.

1385
01:36:15,681 --> 01:36:19,173
Well, I always, always arranged
Mr. Morris' things.

1386
01:36:19,385 --> 01:36:22,650
After he went to bed.
You were there before.

1387
01:36:22,855 --> 01:36:26,052
How would I get out?
All three doors were chain-locked.

1388
01:36:44,377 --> 01:36:46,572
Through Vince's room.

1389
01:36:48,014 --> 01:36:49,572
Then, the next morning...

1390
01:36:49,782 --> 01:36:53,081
<i>... you must have chain-locked the
door before you went to wake him up.</i>

1391
01:36:57,189 --> 01:36:59,316
Fuck!

1392
01:37:02,395 --> 01:37:04,795
Lanny let me read the first chapter.

1393
01:37:04,997 --> 01:37:07,329
Vince sent me the second.

1394
01:37:09,936 --> 01:37:11,801
And you stole this.

1395
01:37:12,004 --> 01:37:13,403
To whet my appetite.

1396
01:37:37,930 --> 01:37:39,659
<i>I wanna write.</i>

1397
01:37:39,865 --> 01:37:41,765
<i>I wanna be a journalist.</i>

1398
01:37:42,401 --> 01:37:45,461
<i>So I could either
use this information...</i>

1399
01:37:46,305 --> 01:37:48,296
<i>... or I could use a lot of money.</i>

1400
01:37:48,507 --> 01:37:50,873
Is that why you killed her?

1401
01:37:52,144 --> 01:37:53,406
To protect them?

1402
01:38:00,753 --> 01:38:04,621
<i>For 15 years...</i>

1403
01:38:04,824 --> 01:38:07,884
<i>... he tormented Vince and Lanny.</i>

1404
01:38:11,464 --> 01:38:15,161
<i>He could never blackmail Vince
while Sally Sanmarco was alive...</i>

1405
01:38:16,068 --> 01:38:20,437
<i>... so he waited until Sally died
to activate his retirement plan:</i>

1406
01:38:23,042 --> 01:38:26,102
<i>A million dollars from Vince.</i>

1407
01:38:26,879 --> 01:38:31,213
<i>A million dollars for the same tape
he offered to me.</i>

1408
01:38:36,122 --> 01:38:39,990
<i>He would never get his money,
and I would never see him again.</i>

1409
01:38:46,031 --> 01:38:48,659
<i>He had taken her life...</i>

1410
01:38:48,868 --> 01:38:51,632
<i>... and with it her mother's heart...</i>

1411
01:38:52,304 --> 01:38:54,602
<i>... and her father's mind.</i>

1412
01:38:56,242 --> 01:38:57,732
<i>And now...</i>

1413
01:38:57,943 --> 01:39:01,174
<i>... all that remained
of Maureen O'Flaherty...</i>

1414
01:39:01,380 --> 01:39:05,407
<i>... was a tree
in her mother's garden.</i>

1415
01:39:20,166 --> 01:39:23,397
Your daughter learned something
about Vince Collins...

1416
01:39:23,602 --> 01:39:26,230
...that he didn't want anyone to know.

1417
01:39:26,505 --> 01:39:28,200
Because of that...

1418
01:39:28,407 --> 01:39:29,965
...she was killed.

1419
01:39:30,176 --> 01:39:33,339
If it's of any small comfort,
she probably didn't suffer.

1420
01:39:33,946 --> 01:39:37,541
I want people
to know about this man.

1421
01:39:38,150 --> 01:39:40,948
I want them to know
why he killed her.

1422
01:39:46,292 --> 01:39:48,453
There is someone in all this...

1423
01:39:48,661 --> 01:39:50,754
...who is totally innocent
of any involvement...

1424
01:39:50,963 --> 01:39:52,863
...in the events of that night...

1425
01:39:53,065 --> 01:39:57,900
...but whose life will be made infinitely
worse if I tell the truth at this time.

1426
01:39:58,938 --> 01:40:02,465
I wanna protect this person
from any further pain.

1427
01:40:05,511 --> 01:40:07,479
I promise you...

1428
01:40:08,047 --> 01:40:11,539
I promise you I will write down
the truth that I've learned...

1429
01:40:11,750 --> 01:40:14,742
...but I have to let matters lie
until this person has died...

1430
01:40:14,954 --> 01:40:17,149
...and the truth
can no longer touch them.

1431
01:40:22,361 --> 01:40:25,455
<i>I saw no indication on her face...</i>

1432
01:40:25,664 --> 01:40:28,224
<i>... that she knew
I was talking about her.</i>

1433
01:41:02,001 --> 01:41:04,595
You're a very special girl.

1434
01:41:12,745 --> 01:41:15,213
Forgive me.

1435
